  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this prospective study with the aim to establish a registry is to learn about the&#xD;
      role of steroid hormones in severely injured patients. The main question it aims to answer is&#xD;
      whether steroid hormones influence morbidity and mortality after severe trauma.&#xD;
&#xD;
      This is a prospective study with the aim to establish a large registry for severely injured&#xD;
      patients and their hormonal status.&#xD;
&#xD;
      Hormone levels will be measured upon arrival in the emergency room and within the following&#xD;
      few days after trauma. Furthermore a detailed questionnaire aims to answer any&#xD;
      hormone-related health questions.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
